Each section can have an image or a video background

Sections:
Dark-text-right: right-justified text (from lg) + left justified image 
Light-text-right: right-justified text (from lg) + left justified image + white overlay on sm to lg

Dark-text-left: left-justified text (from lg) + right justified image 
Dark-text-right: right-justified text (from lg) + left justified image 

Dark-text-center: center-justified text (from lg) + center justified image 
Light-text-center: center-justified text (from lg) + center justified image + white overlay on sm to lg


Section elements:
section title + span class
Section paragraph
Max 2 buttons 

Attention
see 
http://kaffa.like-themes.com/home-parallax/ the jpeg is right justified even on large/mobile + overlay on mobile


